text: Fazenda is a type of plantion in colonial Brazil. Fazenda may also refer to: * Fazenda (Lajes das Flores), a parish in the Azores * Fazenda, Cape Verde, a settlement in Cabo Verde * Fazenda, Praia, a subdivision of Praia, Cabo Verde * "(Ministry of) Fazenda", former name of: ** Ministry of the Economy (Brazil) ** Ministry of Finance (Portugal) * Louise Fazenda, American film actress * Ricardo Fazenda, Portuguese footballer == See also == * * A Fazenda, a Brazilian reality TV show
